for 20 minutes and it was all
very scientific, you know?

08:24.371 --> 08:25.573
How was it?

08:26.173 --> 08:27.808
Oh! Not good.

08:27.908 --> 08:31.211
Just not good, you know?
Pressed our mouths together
and kind of

08:31.311 --> 08:32.913
