a pretty damn good view.

17:34.187 --> 17:35.622
Shit.

18:02.449 --> 18:03.750
Harry.

18:03.850 --> 18:07.154
Look, we don't
have to do this.

18:07.187 --> 18:12.058
I'm sorry, okay?
